         <abstract>
            <p>A stable second-order unconstrained minimization algorithm with quadratic termination is given. The algorithm does not require any one-dimensional minimizations. Computational results presented indicate that the performance of this algorithm compares favorably with other well-known unconstrained minimization algorithms.</p>
          </abstract>
